						               													<description>You wake up on a desolate island, your clothes are soaked &amp;amp; the last thing you remember is looking out your ships&amp;rsquo; deck as a storm tossed it about in the ocean. Far to the east of the island, you see your cargo of colourful rafts gently nudging the shore. The adventurer in you awakens!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;On your turn each player gets 3 actions: Dice Roll, Path Bending and Movement. Based on the colours rolled on the first action the player can choose rafts for the next action where they place and remove rafts from anyones path. The player can either move free to a raft of the same colour or roll a Draft to move to a raft of another colour. Attack other players by rolling any colour doubles and skip a raft on double draft.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Create your own path by building, breaking &amp;amp; jumping across the colourful rafts to make your way back to the Shore. The first player to reach shore wins the game!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Roll the dice to test your luck in this sweet and brutal game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
